<h2>Why This Matters</h2>

<p>System prompt leakage by itself is rated Medium — the information is sensitive but the immediate impact is limited. However, it dramatically enables other attacks. Knowing your system prompt allows an attacker to craft more targeted prompt injections, identify high-value data sources the agent can access, and find gaps in your AI's instruction coverage.</p>

